clinical_study.brief_title: Refitting Frequent Replacement Lens Wearers Into Clariti 1 Day And 1-Day Acuvue Moist Daily Disposable Spherical Lenses
clinical_study.official_title: Refitting Frequent Replacement Lens Wearers Into Clariti 1 Day And 1-Day Acuvue Moist Daily Disposable Spherical Lenses (BEAGLE 2)

brief_summary.textblock: The objective of the study is to evaluate and compare the performance of somofilcon A to etafilcon A when worn on a daily disposable wear modality over a period of approximately one week.

detailed_description.textblock: The study is a prospective, double masked (investigator and participant), bilateral, randomized, cross-over dispensing study, which evaluates somofilcon A (test lens) and etafilcon A (control lens).
